\begin_inset Formula $T_{4}\left(\left[\begin{array}{c}
2\\
2
\end{array}\right]\right)=\left[\begin{array}{c}
1\\
1
\end{array}\right]+\left[\begin{array}{c}
1\\
0
\end{array}\right]=\left[\begin{array}{c}
