 right square of the dissection.
 Letting 
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

 be the 
\begin_inset Formula $2$
\end_inset

 by 
\begin_inset Formula $2$
\end_inset

 square with opposite corners 
\begin_inset Formula $(0,0)$
\end_inset

